  <div class="c-entry-hero__content l-segment l-feature">
    
    
    <h1 class="c-page-title">The awakening of Norman Rockwell </h1>

    <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">For decades, the artist’s Saturday Evening Post covers championed a retrograde view of America. This is the story of the politically turbulent 1960s, a singular painting, and Rockwell’s unlikely change of heart.</p>

    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
        By
        <span class="c-byline__item">
          
            
            <a href="https://www.vox.com/users/tomcarson" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Tom Carson</span></a>
          
        </span>
      
      
      <span class="c-byline__item">
        
            Updated
        
        <time class="c-byline__item" data-ui="timestamp" datetime="2020-02-26T14:00:00">
          Feb 26, 2020,  9:00am EST
        </time>
      </span>
      
      
      
    
    
    
